high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the sink, then go to the left to face the counter adjacent to the sink.
Open the left cabinet beneath the counter and take out the plate from inside.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Clean the plate inside the sink.
Go to your left, then turn around to face the counter.
Put the plate on the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left and cross the room to stand at the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the cabinet on the bottom left and take the plate out.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the plate in the sink and turn the water on and then off and take the plate out again.
Turn and face to the right.
Put the plate down on the sink to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on the counter.

high_descs: take the dirty pan from the cabinet below the counter
take the pan to the sink
wash the pan in the sink
take the pan to the counter to the right
put the pan on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: wash the dirty pan in the cabinet then put it on the counter
